I don't speak Jewish.

03:31.011 --> 03:33.547
Oh, that was
embarrassing.

03:33.647 --> 03:34.982
Mmm. But don't worry.

03:35.082 --> 03:36.950
They're in tight now.

03:37.050 --> 03:38.752
[chuckling]

03:38.852 --> 03:39.920
