why don't you hurry up

03:40.020 --> 03:41.589
and change for lunch?

03:43.457 --> 03:44.992
This is what
I'm wearing to lunch.

03:45.092 --> 03:46.760
Oh!

03:46.860 --> 03:50.398
We're going to
the lesbian bar?

03:50.498 --> 03:51.899
We could.

03:51.999 --> 03:55.569
I hear the Honey Bucket
has a great spread.

04:02.443 --> 04:05.479
