outfit, Mom.

04:05.579 --> 04:06.980
This shirt costs
more than your wig.

04:08.849 --> 04:10.484
Oh, well, I like it
'cause it's cheap.

04:10.584 --> 04:13.421
You can throw it
in the dishwasher.

04:13.521 --> 04:15.323
Well, that would
probably explain

04:15.423 --> 04:18.826
this corn
on the cob holder.

04:18.926 --> 04:21.362
Ah!
Here you go.

04:21.462 --> 04:24.365
Can we just go to lunch?

04:24.465 --> 04:25.766
Oh, well,
I hope you take me

04:25.866 --> 04:28.268
