Brown water.

05:37.638 --> 05:42.376
Rats and roaches." Juicy!

05:42.476 --> 05:46.780
So, what morally bankrupt
monster am I taking down?

05:46.880 --> 05:49.450
Karen Walker.

05:50.918 --> 05:53.787
Yep, that sounds
about right.

05:56.156 --> 05:59.993
Ugh! Thank God she's gone.

06:00.093 --> 06:00.828
All that's left of her

06:00.928 --> 06:05.065
are a few strands
of pink horse hair

06:05.165 --> 06:08.502
and a few flecks
of Polident.

06:08.602 --> 06:11.104
Yeah. Thank God
that's over.

06:11.204 --> 06:12.606
