but I'm gonna be honest.

12:01.288 --> 12:03.456
Oh, forget it.

12:05.125 --> 12:06.259
What are you up to?

12:06.359 --> 12:08.862
Well, I got big news.

12:08.962 --> 12:10.163
I finally did it.

12:10.263 --> 12:12.365
Today I stuck it
to the Man.

12:12.465 --> 12:16.503
Oh, finally. That was
a long dry spell.

12:18.471 --> 12:20.473
Not that. Karen.

12:20.573 --> 12:23.210
I got the judge
to order her to pay

12:23.310 --> 12:25.178
for all the improvements
to that building she owns.

12:25.278 --> 12:28.782
Oh. That's great.
Good for you.

12:28.882 --> 12:30.984
Yeah, good for the people.

12:31.084 --> 12:33.253
And, uh, I also get him
to sentence her

12:33.353 --> 12:34.154
to live in the building
for a week.

12:34.254 --> 12:38.158
Really? That sounds
kinds of harsh.

12:38.258 --> 12:41.261
It's not harsh, Grace.
It's my job.

12:41.361 --> 12:43.864
I dole out justice
Truman style.

12:46.166 --> 12:47.935
Why can't you just say
you go to work

12:48.035 --> 12:50.070
like everyone else?

12:50.170 --> 12:54.908
I don't say "I dole out
furniture Adler style."

12:55.008 --> 12:57.444
Trust me.
It's the right thing to do.

12:57.544 --> 12:59.246
You know, maybe if she spends
a little time in the building

12:59.346 --> 13:01.481
it'll give her a chance
to really look at herself.

13:01.581 --> 13:02.916
Think about
what she's done.

13:03.016 --> 13:05.152
Have you really
looked at yourself?

13:05.252 --> 13:07.054
What's that supposed
to mean?

13:07.154 --> 13:09.022
I mean,
what are you doing?

13:09.122 --> 13:10.891
You got her to pay
for something

13:10.991 --> 13:13.460
