about until you told her.

13:13.560 --> 13:15.395
Why wasn't that enough?

13:15.495 --> 13:18.031
Well, it's complicated.

13:18.131 --> 13:20.333
Doesn't sound complicated.

13:20.433 --> 13:22.269
I mean, you took the job
because you wanted

13:22.369 --> 13:24.171
to become more
compassionate, right?

13:24.271 --> 13:25.305
Yeah, I did.

13:26.239 --> 13:27.340
