14:00.240 --> 14:01.408
All right, now all
you have to do

14:02.475 --> 14:04.277
is not take the bait when
your mother provokes you.

14:04.377 --> 14:06.113
All right?
Now, I'll be Bobbi

14:06.213 --> 14:07.014
and you be you.

14:07.114 --> 14:10.417
And no matter
what I say, don't react.

14:10.517 --> 14:13.253
Just sit there, relax,
and do nothing.

14:13.353 --> 14:15.923
