instead of the hook.

14:36.076 --> 14:40.013
The inexplicably
good legs.

14:40.113 --> 14:42.215
And I'm Bobbi.
Aah!

14:46.353 --> 14:47.887
Grace, focus!

14:47.988 --> 14:50.657
Now remember,
no matter what I say,

14:50.757 --> 14:53.193
