to do this a few more times.

15:40.507 --> 15:43.343
All right, Grace.
I've had it with you.

15:43.443 --> 15:46.479
You are unteachable!
And you ruined my wig!

15:46.579 --> 15:49.282
I don't even know if these
curls are resetable.

15:49.382 --> 15:51.985
